explanation: [0-0] Two men are standing on grass, with a winding path and blue sky behind them. The man on the left is wearing a yellow shirt and blue jeans, while the man on the right is wearing a white shirt and black shorts. Both men are holding picks, and above their heads are green, fully charged power bars. Red subtitles at the top of the video read "Would you help him?"

[0-10] Then, as they dig into the ground together, a house rises from the earth. The power bar above the man on the left gradually decreases, changing color from green to yellow, orange, and finally red as he becomes exhausted. Meanwhile, the power bar above the man on the right also decreases by one bar, but he continues to dig, and his house is taller than the one on the left. A red arrow then points to the man in yellow, and the man in white covers his face with his hands in shock. The camera zooms in on the man in white, who jumps down from his roof happily.
